text:
Oh, that magazine...!
Hana and Haruki are in it too...!

I ended up buying plenty for everyone...
It seems we were thinking the same thing...

Since it's Luca on the cover...
I thought everyone would want to read it...!

There are so many, what should we do...? Should I stack
them here with a note saying "Feel free to take one"...?
Hmm, Luca might get upset about that, you think...?

I could write "Please don't mind Luca-chan"
or something like that...!
That might make her more curious...

Hehe... hehehe...! With all these magazines,
it feels like we have a fan club, doesn't it...?
